Controlpanel
-------------------

This program is a gui for mpd and zsnes. The main purpose is to provide an
intface controllable with a joystick. This makes it possible to easily build a
music control/gaming station with one control device.


Installation
-------------------

comming soon


Dependences
-------------------

Python librarys

- pygame
- pympd

External programs
- znes


